============================================================
 WebRTC Application that enables peer-to-peer communication.
============================================================

Instructions : 
* Enter the database and authentication details in `init.php`.
* To run the application, open up index.html in Chrome Canary(/Dev Channel) [https://tools.google.com/dlpage/chromesxs?platform=win].

To Do :
* Convert the server-side code from PHP to node.js.
* Get rid off AJAX Polling using Web Sockets.
* And last but not definitely the least, tidy up the JS code and make the page prettier.